38
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:26,280
THE FIRST HIGH SCHOOL
SPECIAL SEMINAR ON PSYCHOLOGY

39
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,840
I noticed

40
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:29,400
that some students were nodding off.

41
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,680
Why?

42
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,280
Did you think what I said earlier

43
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,720
was boring?

44
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,960
Then let's talk

45
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:37,680
about something more interesting.

46
00:02:39,320 --> 00:02:40,600
What is considered interesting?

47
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,840
You usually listen to music, right?

48
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,600
Who do you like listening to?

49
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:49,240
-Of course.
-Jay Chou!

50
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,960
You have a pretty good taste.

51
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:57,080
