154
00:09:01,560 --> 00:09:02,840
How could you secretly sneak

155
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:05,440
into another class

156
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:06,920
at night like that?

157
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,600
I didn't.

158
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:15,680
Jiang Jia, are you dumb?

159
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:17,640
If you don't leave your name on the gift,

160
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,200
how will the receiver know who sent it?

161
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,840
That doesn't matter to me

162
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:24,080
as long as they receive the gift.

163
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,920
You're such a coward at times.

164
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,600
You don't have a crush.

165
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,800
You wouldn't understand.

166
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:33,240
Whatever.

167
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:34,440
Why wouldn't I understand?

168
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,200
Whatever.

169
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:39,120
Are you sure
your keys are in the classroom?

170
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,240
-Someone is coming.
-I'm sure.

171
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,080
I found them.

172
00:10:02,160 --> 00:10:04,000
Luckily, you didn't lose them outside.
Let's go.

173
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,000
Let's go.

174
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,920
Thank goodness. We weren't seen.

175
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,400
What are you staring at?

176
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,720
Are you stunned?

177
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:41,840
Nonsense.

178
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:45,400
I didn't even want to hide.

179
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,960
We weren't doing anything bad.

180
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:51,960
Then why are you blushing?

181
00:10:52,040 --> 00:10:53,040
I'm not.

182
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:54,640
It got scratched.

183
00:10:55,280 --> 00:10:56,280
It was all your fault.

184
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,560
You just had to hide.

185
00:10:58,720 --> 00:11:00,040
Have you forgotten about the time

186
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,560
Zaizai was accused of stealing money?

187
00:11:01,640 --> 00:11:03,560
I don't want to cause misunderstandings.

188
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,280
Still,

189
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:09,320
wouldn't the consequences be worse

190
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,680
if we both got caught hiding?

191
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,640
Why?

192
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:18,160
The school has been
cracking down on puppy love.

193
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:22,960
Who would be so unkind to themselves
as to be involved with you?

194
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,680
You're so clumsy.

195
