going abroad?

199
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:38,920
That's all for today's class.

200
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,440
A round of applause, please.

201
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:43,480
All right. Thank you for the support!

202
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,000
Thank you

203
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,280
for giving me your attention.

204
00:12:47,800 --> 00:12:48,680
This session

205
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:51,360
was mainly about the eyes.

206
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:53,280
It's not something you can learn

207
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,680
in a day or two.

208
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:55,880
So make sure

209
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,800
to practice it more at home.

210
00:12:57,880 --> 00:13:00,760
One day, your eyes will be like mine,

211
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,360
bright

212
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,560
and piercing.

213
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,280
By the way,

214
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,880
your senior schoolmate, Shen Qianyu,

215
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:13,280
will be leaving the country soon.

216
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:15,400
He has about a week left.

217
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:18,120
You all should cherish your time with him.

218
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,560
So then...

219
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:21,160
Is Qianyu going abroad?

220
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,120
That's right.

221
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,960
-He...
-It's because of my parents' job transfer.

222
00:13:24,040 --> 00:13:25,480
I had no choice.

223
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:26,440
Yes, I think...

224
00:13:26,520 --> 00:13:28,800
Does the countdown start today?

225
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,600
Hold on. You guys keep interrupting me.

226
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:33,040
I seem to be the extra in this class.

227
00:13:33,640 --> 00:13:35,400
You guys have a chat and catch up.

228
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:39,880
Though I haven't known you for very long,

229
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,200
I'm still grateful to all of you

230
00:13:41,280 --> 00:13:42,640
for joining the Drama Club.

231
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,320
I hope I'll have the chance to see you

232
00:13:45,400 --> 00:13:46,800
on a bigger stage in the future.

233
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:48,760
Keep it up.

234
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,040
Did you find out about it yesterday?

235
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:07,000
Yes.

236
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,480
When I went to drop off the stars,

237
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:11,400
I accidentally saw the documents
he had prepared for his departure.

238
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,960
Why is it so sudden?

239
00:14:15,640 --> 00:14:16,840
Zaizai, I've made up my mind.

240
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:18,920
About what?

241
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,960
I didn't give him the stars in person

242
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:23,720
because I thought
we had a lot of time left

243
00:14:23,800 --> 00:14:25,120
and could slowly get to know each other.

244
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,480
But there is no time now.

245
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:28,920
I don't want to have any regrets.

246
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:32,160
So what do you plan to do?

247
00:14:36,800 --> 00:14:38,000
<i>Did you know</i>

248
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:40,120
<i>that we will meet 29,2 million people</i>

249
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,440
<i>in our lifetime?</i>

250
00:14:41,520 --> 00:14:42,720
<i>When I think about it,</i>

251
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:44,760
<i>meeting you at the age of 16</i>

252
00:14:44,840 --> 00:14:46,880
<i>should be one
of my life's few lucky moments.</i>

253
00:14:47,720 --> 00:14:49,120
<i>The first time I saw you,</i>

254
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,480
<i>you were sitting on the grass
and playing the guitar.</i>

255
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:53,200
<i>There were so many people around,</i>

256
00:14:53,280 --> 00:14:54,960
<i>but I saw you right away.</i>

257
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,520
"I couldn't help

258
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:58,680
but start to get close to you.

259
00:14:58,760 --> 00:15:00,280
I asked around for your grade and class

260
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,800
and learned about your preferences.

261
00:15:01,880 --> 00:15:05,240
